  "tasbihatZahraSubtitle": "Ka dib salaad kasta · 100 kuul",
  "tasbihatZahraOriginLabel": "Asal",
  "tasbihatZahraHadith": "Marwo Faaduma al-Zahra (sa) waxay Nabiga ﷺ ka codsatay adeegto. Wuxuu yiri: \"Miyaanan ku tusin wax ka khayr badan taas? Akhri Subḥānallāh 33 jeer, Alḥamdulillāh 33 jeer, iyo Allāhu Akbar 34 jeer salaad kasta ka dib. Taasi waxay kuu dhaantaa adeegto.\"",
  "tasbihatZahraHadithSource": "— Bihar al-Anwār, Jilid 85",
  "tasbihatZahraOpenCounter": "Fur Tiriyaha Tasbīḥ",
  "tasbihatDuasTitle": "DUCOOYINKA LA TALIYEY",
  "tasbihatDuasSubtitle": "Ka dib markaad dhamayso salaaddaada",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiTitle": "Āyat al-Kursī",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiWhen": "Salaad kasta oo faral ah ka dib",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiSource": "Suurat al-Baqarah 2:255",
  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiNote": "Qofkii akhriya Āyat al-Kursī salaad kasta oo faral ah ka dib, wax u dhexeeya isaga iyo jannada ma jiraan marka laga reebo geerida. Imam al-Bāqir (a) wuxuu sheegay inay ka mid tahay aayadaha ugu waaweyn Qur’aanka.",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatTitle": "Ṣalawāt",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatWhen": "Salaad kasta ka dib · waxay xidhaysaa dhammaan ducooyinka",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatSource": "Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) — Al-Kāfī",
  "tasbihatDuaSalawatNote": "Dirista salaanta iyo naxariista Nabiga ﷺ iyo ehelkiisa daahirka ah (Āl Muḥammad) waxaa lagu taliyaa si loogu soo xiro dua kasta. Imam al-Ṣādiq (a) wuxuu yiri: \"Dua kasta way hakataa ilaa aad salawaat u dirto Muḥammad iyo ehelkiisa.\"",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajTitle": "Duʿā al-Faraj",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajWhen": "Salaad kasta ka dib · loogu talagalay Imaamka waqtigeenna",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajSource": "Waxaa baray Imam al-Ḥasan al-ʿAskarī (a)",
  "tasbihatDuaFarajNote": "Dua loogu baryayo soo muuqashada Imam al-Mahdī (af), Imaamka 12aad, oo uu baray aabbihii. Waxaa maalin kasta akhriya Shiicada ka dib salaad kasta oo calaamad u ah jacaylka Imaamka nool.",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaTitle": "Tasbīḥda Marwo Fāṭima",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaWhen": "Ka dib Maghrib & Isha · si gaar ah ayaa loogu taliyaa",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaSource": "Imam al-Bāqir (a) — Biḥār al-Anwār",
  "tasbihatDuaTasbihFatimaNote": "Imam al-Bāqir (a) wuxuu sheegay in akhrinta Tasbīḥ al-Zahrā ka dib Isha ka hor hurdada ay ka khayr badan tahay 1000 rakaaco oo salaad sunno ah. Iftiinkeedu wuxuu u kacaa samooyinka.",
